@startuml class_calculator

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Calculator {
    - _history : list[dict]
    --
    + __init__() : None
    - _record_history(operand1, operator: str, operand2, result) : None
    + get_history() : list[dict]
    .. Basic Arithmetic ..
    + add(a, b) : object
    + subtract(a, b) : object
    + multiply(a, b) : object
    + divide(a, b) : object
    .. Power / Root ..
    + power(base: float, exponent: float) : float
    + square(x: float) : float
    + cube(x: float) : float
    + square_root(x: float) : float
    + cube_root(x: float) : float
    .. Logarithmic ..
    + natural_log(x: float) : float
    + log_base_10(x: float) : float
    .. Factorial ..
    + factorial(n: int) : int
}

note right of Calculator::_history
  Stores one dict per operation:
  {operand1, operator, operand2, result}
  operand2 is None for unary ops.
end note

note right of Calculator::square_root
  Raises ValueError if x < 0.
  Delegates to math.sqrt(x).
end note

note right of Calculator::natural_log
  Raises ValueError if x <= 0.
  Delegates to math.log(x).
end note

note right of Calculator::factorial
  Raises TypeError if n is bool or non-int.
  Raises ValueError if n < 0.
end note

class InputValidator {
    + validate_operation(operation: str) : None
    + validate_operand_count(operation: str, operands: list) : None
    + validate(operation: str, operands: list) : None
}

class ExpressionParser {
    - _coerce_numeric(token: str) : Numeric
    + parse(raw_input: str) : tuple
}

class RetryConfig <<dataclass>> {
    + max_retries : int = 3
}

class CalculatorREPL {
    - _calculator : Calculator
    - _parser : ExpressionParser
    - _validator : InputValidator
    - _retry_config : RetryConfig
    - _EXIT_COMMANDS : frozenset
    --
    + __init__(calculator: Calculator, retry_config: RetryConfig | None) : None
    - _dispatch(operation: str, operands: list) : Numeric
    - _evaluate(raw_input: str) : str
    + run() : None
}

CalculatorREPL *--> Calculator : _calculator
CalculatorREPL *--> ExpressionParser : _parser
CalculatorREPL *--> InputValidator : _validator
CalculatorREPL o--> RetryConfig : _retry_config

class "math" <<stdlib>> {
    + sqrt(x) : float
    + log(x) : float
    + log10(x) : float
    + copysign(mag, sign) : float
}

Calculator ..> "math" : uses

@enduml
